description: This file serves as the entry point for a React web application. It imports core React modules, a CSS file for styling, and the main App component. It initializes the React DOM by creating a root and rendering the App component within a strict mode for highlighting potential problems.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the created root.
